To determine if you are dealing with the first entry of a given month, you will need to query your db table for the `MAX()` serial number -- lets refer to that value as php variable `$max`.

    $Ym = date(&#39;Ym&#39;);
    if (strpos($max, $Ym) === 0) {
        ++$max;
    } else {
        $max = $Ym . &#39;001&#39;;
    }

Then use the new `$max` in your INSERT query.

...and of course, there is the very real concern of a &quot;race condition&quot; creating conflicting serial numbers.
